OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer welcomed the US-Iran
OL,8,Fpeace deal as a "hugely important step
OL,9,Fforward in ending the war" as he
OL,10,Fstressed that the Strait of Hormuz
OL,11,Fmust remain "fully and permanently
OL,12,Fopen".
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister congratulated
OL,15,FDonald Trump and key mediators on the
OL,16,F"breakthrough" after the US president
OL,17,Fsaid an agreement "is now complete"
OL,18,Fand the Strait of Hormuz oil and gas
OL,19,Fshipping route is to be reopened
OL,20,Fwithout tolls.
OL,26,@pD@QOUqD@ZO]sD@MOUtD@EO]xD@AOUxD@NO]yD@
OL,26,ASOUyD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
