FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FSir Keir said in a statement: "I
OL,8,Fwarmly welcome today's agreement
OL,9,Freached between the United States and
OL,10,FIran.
OL,12,F"This is a hugely important step
OL,13,Fforward in ending the war, ensuring
OL,14,Fregional stability, and re-opening the
OL,15,FStrait of Hormuz."
OL,26,@oD@_OUtD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FHe continued: "Attention must now turn
OL,8,Fto fully implementing the memorandum
OL,9,Fof understanding to ensure the Strait
OL,10,Freopens and remains fully and
OL,11,Fpermanently open, and that the
OL,12,Fdetailed elements of the nuclear
OL,13,Fagreement are finalised. We stand
OL,14,Fready to support the technical talks
OL,15,Fthat will now begin. Our priority is
OL,16,Fthat this becomes a durable and
OL,17,Flasting peace, and we will work with
OL,18,Finternational partners to support that.
OL,26,@oD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"We are clear that toll-free freedom
OL,8,Fof navigation must now be restored in
OL,9,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, to begin easing
OL,10,Fthe severe economic impacts that have
OL,11,Fbeen felt for several months ` on
OL,12,Ffamilies here in the UK and around the
OL,13,Fworld."
OL,15,FSir Keir said the UK would stand up
OL,16,Fthe defensive mission led by Britain
OL,17,Fand France to assist with demining the
OL,18,FStrait of Hormuz once the conflict is
OL,19,Fpaused.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"For any peace to endure, it is
OL,8,Fessential that the commitments made,
OL,9,Fparticularly in relation to Iran's
OL,10,Fnuclear programme, are robust,
OL,11,Fverifiable, and fully implemented. It
OL,12,Fremains the UK's firm and longstanding
OL,13,Fposition that Iran must never have a
OL,14,Fnuclear weapon."
OL,16,FIn a joint statement with the leaders
OL,17,Fof France, Germany and Italy, Sir Keir
OL,18,Falso said: "We are prepared to lift
OL,19,Frelevant sanctions in response to
OL,20,Fclear, verifiable steps by Iran on its
OL,21,Fnuclear programme."
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@PO]zD@LOU}D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
