OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe so-called E4 also underlined the
OL,8,Fimportance of "unconditional and
OL,9,Funrestricted freedom of navigation" in
OL,10,Fthe strait, and called for the accord
OL,11,Fto be "implemented rapidly and
OL,12,Fcomprehensively".
OL,14,FMr Trump earlier said a deal had been
OL,15,Freached and that he was authorising an
OL,16,Fend to the US naval blockade of
OL,17,FIranian ports in the Strait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@pD@OOUqD@cO]sD@GOUtD@PO]
