OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe American leader, who is
OL,8,Fcelebrating his 80th birthday, wrote
OL,9,Fon his Truth Social platform on
OL,10,FSunday: "The Deal with the Islamic
OL,11,FRepublic of Iran is now complete.
OL,13,F"Congratulations to all!
OL,15,F"I hereby fully authorize the toll
OL,16,Ffree opening of the Strait of Hormuz,
OL,17,Fand, simultaneously herewith,
OL,18,Fauthorize the immediate removal of the
OL,19,FUnited States Naval blockade.
OL,26,@rD@IOUuD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
