OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"Ships of the World, start your
OL,8,Fengines. Let the oil flow!"
OL,10,FShehbaz Sharif, the prime minister of
OL,11,FPakistan, which has been mediating in
OL,12,Fthe conflict, said the accord covered
OL,13,FLebanon.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@[O]
