PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FHe wrote on X: "Following intensive
OL,8,Ftalks, we are pleased to announce that
OL,9,Fthe Peace Deal between the United
OL,10,FStates of America and Islamic Republic
OL,11,Fof Iran has been REACHED. Both sides
OL,12,Fhave declared the immediate and
OL,13,Fpermanent termination of military
OL,14,Foperations on all fronts, including in
OL,15,FLebanon.
OL,17,F"The official signing ceremony will be
OL,18,Fon Friday, 19 June in Switzerland."
OL,26,@oD@POUyD@AOUzD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
