CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FHe added that "mediators will
OL,8,Ffacilitate a series of meetings this
OL,9,Fweek".
OL,11,F"These pre-implementation discussions
OL,12,Fwill lay the foundation for the
OL,13,Ftechnical talks and the official
OL,14,Fsigning ceremony."
OL,16,FFull details of the deal did not
OL,17,Fimmediately emerge and it was unclear
OL,18,Fhow soon the Strait of Hormuz could
OL,19,Freopen to all vessels.
OL,26,@oD@OOUqD@EO]sD@AOUvD@RO]
