OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FCentral to the negotiations has been
OL,8,FIran's stranglehold on the critical
OL,9,Fwaterway, which has disrupted global
OL,10,Foil and gas supplies and driven up
OL,11,Ffuel and food prices.
OL,13,FAnother flashpoint has been Tehran's
OL,14,Fnuclear plans, which it insists are
OL,15,Fpeaceful but the US and Israel fear
OL,16,Fcould be used to build a weapon due to
OL,17,Fits stockpile of highly enriched
OL,18,Furanium.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
