CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,FThe US president is expected to
OL,8,Fdiscuss plans with allies during next
OL,9,Fweek's G7 summit in France.
OL,11,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,12,Fthe UK stands "ready to help" develop
OL,13,Fthe US-Iran agreement into "a lasting
OL,14,Fpeace".
OL,16,FShe said: "I strongly welcome the
OL,17,Fannouncement of an agreement between
OL,18,Fthe US and Iran.
OL,26,@tD@OOUtD@]O]uD@\OUvD@FO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"It is vital that toll-free freedom of
OL,8,Fnavigation through the Strait of
OL,9,FHormuz is swiftly restored, so
OL,10,Finternational shipping can get moving
OL,11,Fagain to help the global economy and
OL,12,Ffamilies here at home.
OL,14,F"The UK stands ready with France and
OL,15,Fother countries to support that
OL,16,Fprocess as needed.
OL,26,@oD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1781488075
OL,3,CStarmer says Strait of Hormuz must
OL,4,Cstay open after Iran-US peace deal
OL,5,Cannounced
OL,7,F"Our longstanding position is that
OL,8,FIran must never be allowed to develop
OL,9,Fa nuclear weapon. The UK is ready to
OL,10,Fsupport the technical work to ensure
OL,11,Fthat vital objective is implemented.
OL,13,F"This agreement is important for
OL,14,Fregional and global security and for
OL,15,Fthe international economy. Thank you
OL,16,Fto all those involved in negotiations
OL,17,Fincluding Pakistan and Qatar. It is
OL,18,Fvital that progress continues ` we
OL,19,Fstand ready to help make it a lasting
OL,20,Fpeace."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
